instructions: put the dinner plate on the table cloth
place the salad plate on top of the dinner plate
put the napkin on top of the dinner plate
place the wine glass in the upper right corner of the table cloth
place the water glass diagonally right from the wine glass
put the salad fork on the left of the plates
put the dinner fork between the plates and the salad fork
put the dinner knife on the right of the plates
put the soup spoon on the right of the knife
